pull_request.title: enable support for specific liboqs releases
pull_request.body: This adds configuration, code and documentation to facilitate building and possibly releasing `oqsprovider` against a specific `liboqs` version (not in line with the respective projects' `main` branch).

pull_request.title: Bump oqs-sys/liboqs from `4916446` to `341cf22`
pull_request.body:
